    "Detailed specification of MPTokenIssuance settings and their impact on ledger state size.",
    "Analysis of potential edge cases in Payment and Clawback transactions involving MPTs.",
    "Performance benchmarks for the new mpt_holders API method."
  ],
  "route": "HOLD_FOR_CHALLENGE",
  "route_confidence": 0.95,
  "validator_work_item": {
    "override_questions": [
      "Does the new MPT token model introduce any risks to ledger consensus or liveness?",
      "Are there any known vulnerabilities in the MPTokenIssuanceCreate or MPTokenAuthorize transactions?",
      "How does the MPT model interact with existing trustline-based tokens in terms of accounting and settlement?"
    ],
    "recommended_validator_action": "Conduct a deep review of the MPTokensV1 specification, focusing on asset-control semantics, transaction processing edge cases, and integration with existing payment and clawback mechanisms. Verify that the new ledger entry types do not introduce state bloat or performance issues.",
    "review_questions": [
      "What are the implications of the new MPToken and MPTokenIssuance ledger entry types on node storage and performance?",
      "How does the MPT model handle transfer fees and clawback mechanisms compared to existing trustlines?",
      "Are there any potential issues with the mpt_holders API method in terms of data consistency or performance?",
      "Does the MPT model introduce any new attack vectors or security risks?"
    ],
    "title": "Review MPTokensV1: New Multi-Purpose Token Standard"
  }
